  <brief_title>Comparison of Effects Between Amlodipine and Hydrochlorothiazide in Combination With Losartan on 24-hr Central Blood Pressure in Hypertensive Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Effects Between Calcium Channel Blocker and Diuretics in Combination With Angiotensin II Receptor Blocker on 24-hr Central Blood Pressure and Vascular Hemodynamic Parameters in Hypertensive Patients Multicenter, Double-blind, Active-controlled, Phase 4 Randomized Trial</official_title>
